Once Gormok is slain, Acidmaw and Dreadscale spawn. These are serpents that
together offer quite the challenge. When one serpent is killed, the
special-attack damage of the other increases by 50%. 

Acidmaw has a fairly weak hit, but it will paralyze the main target very
frequently, as well as paralyzing a random target every now and then. As can be
seen from hurtme's reports, there are periods where the tank can be chain-
paralyzed. If you compare the below reports, it can be seen that Acidmaw causes
paralyzes almost 2/3 of the time.

While Acidmaw's role is to basically remove one player from combat and be an
annoyance for the oter party members, Dreadscale is the damage dealer. Very
frequently Dreadscale will spray every attacker with a damage-over-time fire
liquid, but it will also deal additional direct-damage to the tank. The fire
damage is cumulative, so Dreadscale must be killed quickly.

When acting together, these two will pose quite the challenge.


