REWARDS 

Once beaten this encounter yields an armoured belt and a special pair of metal
gloves. The belt has 4 ac and +2 con. Its weight is 3, and it has a value of
2222, so it should both take up valuable inventory space, but also cost a
little extra to repair.

The gloves are +2 str, but if worn without wielding any weapon or wearing a
shield, they will spawn and force-wield a pair of fist weapons. These weapons
give +1 dex each, and have 0 weight. During combat, the weapons may proc both
the fire of Dreadscale and the toxin of Acidmaw. Average damage is ~42.29 with
procs, and ~33.76 if no_special_attack is set. About 1 in 10 attack is blocked
due to the toxin effect.

The gloves are quite awesome, but presumably this is ok as they occupy both
glove, shield, left and right hand slots to work. Furthermore, whenever the
gloves are removed, the weapons are destroyed, causing any enchantment to wear
off.

===> Round: 236  Damage: 14  Total: 10023  Average: 42.29  Max: 47
